<p><strong>Why this step matters:</strong> Content creates new entry points to your website. Every blog post targeting a local keyword is another chance to appear in search results. Over 6-12 months, 100+ posts create a content moat that competitors cannot match without an equal investment.</p>
<h2>Step 7: Track Performance and Improve</h2>
<p>Everything above is useless if you do not measure what is working. Most local businesses never look at their data. That is why they do not improve.</p>
<h3>What to Track Monthly</h3>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
